{"tid":1074692,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[三國L小知識］其實蜀國唔只得諸葛亮一位謀士","createTime":"2019-03-23T14:37:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T02:43:47.000Z","uid":191650,"like":4,"dislike":61,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"48681713c85a3087dd1abb65723beb04bd3ccce9","tid":1074692,"uid":191650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T14:37:04.000Z","msg":"有一位叫<span style=\"color: red;\">鳳雛龐統</span>嘅人，睇過三國史嘅肯定知。其實佢好多嘢都唔輸諸葛亮，<span style=\"color: red;\">竟然係輸樣衰</span> 下面係佢以下功績<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1、掛劍夜讀孫吳兵法，可見龐統文武雙全，勤奮好學；<br />\n2、面見孫權，不卑不亢，有文人傲骨；<br />\n3、識破諸葛亮弔孝之計；<br />\n4、調解黃忠魏延爭功；<br />\n5、辦事果斷，喝斬二將；<br />\n6、先斬後奏，令魏延舞劍；<br />\n7、肚量寬廣，不記劉備酒後之言；<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有獻連環計，使曹操戰船用鐵索連環，促使周郎火燒赤壁。能夠隻身騙得<br />\n蔣幹信任，介紹到曹營，施展辯才，誇耀曹操功績，取得曹操信任，與眾謀士同說兵<br />\n<br />\n佢根本死得太早同樣衰而唔受劉備重用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想睇更多pm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a85de1f037cd7089c2379ac4896c4039a1114c1","tid":1074692,"uid":43178,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T14:38:32.000Z","msg":"Pmed"},{"pid":"780ac2e697c694d9893f4bf59d5166515fe80ba8","tid":1074692,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T14:42:02.000Z","msg":"田豫"},{"pid":"acbc9e4c4940795bcbc927ea674e34d00bac3e36","tid":1074692,"uid":191650,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"780ac2e697c694d9893f4bf59d5166515fe80ba8","tid":1074692,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T14:42:02.000Z","msg":"田豫"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T14:43:17.000Z","msg":"佢都唔輸趙雲<br />\n<br />\n而且幾好人"},{"pid":"46d0502792d5af471cafb162ce4cc20e0a6c73a7","tid":1074692,"uid":53672,"like":17,"dislike":8,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T14:44:22.000Z","msg":"演義撚彈開啦"},{"pid":"61e9f1d5262ed93d26de06b000e5e72ed93ab281","tid":1074692,"uid":154756,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-